      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LIL COCKATOO (1) showed blistering pace early and gave a sight when in the minors, beaten one length over 390m this track in 22.84. Capable of going well again. SEKIRO (2) was well fancied last time and led throughout to score (23.04) at this track in a Maiden over 390m. One of the leading chances again. GOT A SPORT (7) turned in a good run last time, finishing in the placings (23.29) at Wagga in a Grade 5. Lines up from box 7 for the first time. The form out of her last race has been franked. Leading chance. QUANTEZ (4) saluted at big odds last time and can go on with it.",
